       <div class="doc-content ng-scope"> <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Auksjonen.no AS, one of Norway's largest websites for auctions.</font></font></p> <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Since 1987, Motorcompaniet AS has operated with traditional auction sales. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In April 2010, the website </font></font><u><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Auksjonen.no was</font></font></u><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> launched. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In January 2012, </font></font><u><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Auksjonen.no</font></font></u><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> AS was established, and in recent years has had very strong growth. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In 2021, we will employ a total of 52 people.</font></font></p> <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Today, we focus on sales for the business community, private individuals, objects for banks and finance companies, as well as the disposal of bankruptcy estates.</font></font></p> <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Through over 30 years of experience in the auction industry, we consider knowledge of what we sell to be very important. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;" class="">Therefore, we place emphasis on employees who have professional knowledge in the various areas such as cars, construction machinery, heavy vehicles, etc. We only want to have good auctions on our site, therefore our auction advisers also focus on quality assurance of the auctions. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We work continuously on this. </font></font><br> <br> <a href="infosenter/menneskene" class="as-link"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">An overview of employees can be found here</font></font></a><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> .</font></font></p> <ul class="circled"> <li><u><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Auksjonen.no</font></font></u><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> is a 100% independent party and has a safe and secure payment solution for both buyer and seller.</font></font></li> <li><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Secure payment is made to our client account with DNB, and settlement is performed by our settlement department, which currently has 8 employees, of which 2 are auditors.</font></font></li> <li><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">You as a bidder should feel secure when you place a bid. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">As a buyer, you always get access to the bid log. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The bidders are anonymised, for the sake of the bidders. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">If you want full access to the bid log, contact one of our employees. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">IP addresses are registered on all bids.</font></font></li> </ul> <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In 2020, more than 26,000 objects were sold, more than 619,000 bids were registered and we had more than 9 million visits and 80 million page views on our website </font></font><u><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">auksjonen.no</font></font></u><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> . </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Our traffic is constantly growing.</font></font></p> <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Auksjonen.no is headquartered at Sem, by the E18 just outside Tønsberg. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Here we have a warehouse of 16,000m2. </font></font><br> <br> <a href="infosenter/" class="as-link"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Here you will find us</font></font></a><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> .</font></font></p> <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">If you have questions about our services, contact one of our employees.</font></font></p> <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Auksjonen.no</font></font></p> </div>
