    <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Privacy is important both for our customers and us in Auksjonen.no AS (hereinafter referred to as "Auksjonen.no", "we" and "us"). </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We are committed to protecting and respecting your privacy, and all our collection and use of personal information is subject to Norwegian privacy laws. </font></font><br><br><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The privacy statement applies to the use of our services associated with Auksjonen.no and visits to our websites. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Here you can e.g. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">read about the purpose of the processing of personal data under the section on what we use the information for (section 5), as well as what information we collect (section 4), how we do it (section 3) and how you can manage your consent to our processing of your personal data (point 9).</font></font><br><br><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">By using Auksjonen.no, you agree that we may collect and process personal information about you as described below. </font></font><br><br><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Your consent - and any subsequent consent - forms our basis for being able to process your personal data. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In certain cases, some of the treatment may also have its basis for treatment in Norwegian law.</font></font></p>
    </div>
